hich will crumble away at their deep-rooted prejudices. In the face of confusion and the choices before them, what will they find...?\"", "summary": "A Light in the Dark is a new, suspense-filled visual novel on PC. A collaboration between CreSpirit, developers of Rabi-Ribi, and the tag team duo of Storia and Narrator, developers focused on visual novels and RPGs.\n\nHaving worked with CreSpirit on Rabi-Ribi and Narrator on Companion, Sekai Project is teaming up with this dream team of developers to bring their new game project to the West!", "themes": [{"id": 31, "name": "Drama"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/a-light-in-the-dark", "videos": [{"id": 18232, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "dgGzlhA4H5A", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dgGzlhA4H5A", "title": "A Light in the Dark PV", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/dgGzlhA4H5A/maxresdefault.jpg"}]}